snippet.title: Laedomanes - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1369870

Laedomanes is a First Person Platformer with Parkour elements. Explore ancient Space Monoliths and face off against the sentient Machines. Collect and use Laedomanes to improve your gear and travel to artificial star systems via the Wormhole.
